ange how often the map changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/af88dd95169b1b2b2956f0a2b72dfaac.poster.avif?t=1746036706\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/af88dd95169b1b2b2956f0a2b72dfaac.webm?t=1746036706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/af88dd95169b1b2b2956f0a2b72dfaac.mp4?t=1746036706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
